reviewText: These are not easy, but if your willing to put in the time you can really improve your playing. Jaimie Humphries is not as polished as Andy James or Danny Gill as video instructors. For example on the the longer scale runs, his verbal walk-thru is a pain to follow. Get yourself a sheet or two of tab paper and write them down as he stumbles through it and you'lll save yourself a lot of headache.
